{"tid":955560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港豬好快全滅】暫停活豬供港支那非洲豬瘟豬場增至18個","createTime":"2018-12-25T13:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T13:46:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb8c80220ef4058925d58d62c26c00cc84206ba","tid":955560,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181225/s00001/f205ae3aecf1fb1a161ae11397a64325.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181225%2Fs00001%2Ff205ae3aecf1fb1a161ae11397a64325.jpg&h=5ba94e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那非洲豬瘟疫情持續，據支那海關總署公布最新「支那供港澳活豬註冊養殖場名單」，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">154個養殖場中</span></span></strong>，因「非洲豬瘟疫區鄰近縣（市、區）」而暫停向香港供應活豬的豬場已增至18個，其中17個豬場位於廣東省，餘下一個在湖北。<br />\n<br />\n暫停向香港供活豬的17個廣東供港場，分別位於珠海、中山、惠州市、河源市及廣州市白雲區<br />\n<br />\n至於3間早前暫停供港的豬場，現已解除封鎖。"},{"pid":"e1ee7052222f29d70d29b9d724125793a550638c","tid":955560,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:42:09.000Z","msg":"殖民政府唔全停支那豬入口<br />\n靠支那自己停出口<br />\n港豬好快就會全滅, 同沙士時係一樣<br />\n<br />\n中華台北島都全停支那豬及豬製品<br />\n殖民政府同支那豬共存亡"},{"pid":"769376f0e1f940a6ee3ab4a61a33c313554d4078","tid":955560,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:43:15.000Z","msg":"等睇支爆"},{"pid":"19acdb04d98ccf34ba21170e32371e18c77e2060","tid":955560,"uid":167832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdb8c80220ef4058925d58d62c26c00cc84206ba","tid":955560,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181225/s00001/f205ae3aecf1fb1a161ae11397a64325.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181225%2Fs00001%2Ff205ae3aecf1fb1a161ae11397a64325.jpg&h=5ba94e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那非洲豬瘟疫情持續，據支那海關總署公布最新「支那供港澳活豬註冊養殖場名單」，<strong><sp